{"id": "22226", "post": "<div class=\"post-22226 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers tag-bitaccel tag-dallas tag-kvm\" id=\"post-22226\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/bitaccel-com-configurable-kvm-virtual-machines-starting-at-7-month/\" rel=\"bookmark\">BitAccel.com \u2013 Configurable KVM Virtual Machines starting at $7/month</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/bitaccel/\" rel=\"tag\">bitaccel</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/dallas/\" rel=\"tag\">dallas</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/kvm/\" rel=\"tag\">kvm</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \"> May 20, 2020 @ 1:18 pm, by Jon Biloh</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIzMDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTUwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMzAwIDE1MCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot\" title=\"BitAccel VPS Hosting\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/bitaccel.png.webp\" alt=\"BitAccel VPS Hosting\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\"></a></p><p>BitAccel was first featured here in <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/bitaccel-3-15month-1gb-openvz-vps-in-buffalo-new-york/\">April 2013</a> and have been posted a total of <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/?s=bitaccel&amp;searchsubmit=Find\">six times</a>. BitAccel recently shared with us their new platform, which enables you to deploy custom virtual machine configurations with just a few clicks. The guys over at BitAccel are working around the clock to improve their product and plan to release many large updates and bug fixes to their platform in the coming weeks, including an entirely redesigned customer portal. There are no predefined, cookie-cutter packages\u2014you can fully configure every option of your virtual machine, from OS, to RAM size, to the exact amount of storage space you need.</p><p>You can pay for their services using a Credit Card or by adding PayPal credit to your account. After payment is added, you can have your machine deployed in just a few clicks. As always, BitAccel stands by its 7-day moneyback guarantee. BitAccel is located in Dallas, Texas.</p><p><strong>The minimum configuration is as follows:</strong></p><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>KVM-VPS-2GB</b></p><ul><li>1 CPU Cores</li><li>2 GB RAM</li><li>50 GB SSD</li><li>1000 Mbps Port</li><li>1 IP Address</li><li><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit;\">1TB Bandwidth</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit;\">KVM</span></li><li>CentOS, Ubuntu, Debian, Alpine</li><li>On Demand Backup and Restore</li><li>$7.00/month</li><li>[<a href=\"https://www.bitaccel.com\">ORDER LINK</a>]</li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p>BitAccel has made a pricing calculator available on their main website:</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIzMDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTM5IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMzAwIDEzOSI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-22228\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/pricing-calc-bitaccel-300x139.png.webp\" alt=\"BitAccel VPS Hosting Price Calculator\" width=\"300\" height=\"139\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/pricing-calc-bitaccel-300x139.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/pricing-calc-bitaccel-1024x475.png.webp 1024w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/pricing-calc-bitaccel-768x357.png.webp 768w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/pricing-calc-bitaccel.png.webp 1499w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"></p><p>Read more for additional information about their virtual machine creation page, network information and additional features!</p><p>Be sure to leave a comment below if you\u2019ve used BitAccel\u2019s service.</p><p><span id=\"more-22226\"></span></p><p>Below is a snapshot of their virtual machine creation page, which shows you the price live as you configure your virtual machine.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIzMDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTQ2IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMzAwIDE0NiI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-22229\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/vm-creation-bitaccel-300x146.png.webp\" alt=\"BitAccel VPS Hosting VPS Creation\" width=\"300\" height=\"146\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/vm-creation-bitaccel-300x146.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/vm-creation-bitaccel-1024x499.png.webp 1024w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/vm-creation-bitaccel-768x374.png.webp 768w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/vm-creation-bitaccel-1536x748.png.webp 1536w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/vm-creation-bitaccel.png.webp 1556w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"></p><p>BitAccel has also provided us a look at their upcoming feature releases in June:</p><ul><li>One-Click Clone VM</li><li>Resize VM</li><li>Virtual Machine Monitoring</li><li>RDNS control</li></ul><p>Give them a try and let us know how things go for you in the comments!</p><p><strong>Network information:</strong></p><p>DC \